                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 701.7341</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Great Britain</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_PWH1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Page</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-10-24T15:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 24 1917, 3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>5655. United States Government has been requested by Government of Montenegro to
                    receive a minister from that country. Assuming that a similar request was made
                    to the British Government by Montenegro the Department desires to know the
                    attitude of the British Government towards this request. Investigate and report
                    promptly.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
